      <meta name="description">Saami speller, Saami spell checker</meta>
   </header>
   <body>
      <p>Below a number of spellchecker extensions for LibreOffice can be
      downloaded. Please note that these extensions are at most beta releases
      for the time being.</p>

      <p>The extensions are built using HFST and Voikko, and specifically the
      LibreOffice-voikko extension. The spellers here are a direct application
      of the normative fst used as a spelling checker (in combination with an
      error model to create suggestions). They thus avoid the problematic
      conversion to Hunspell or other list-based formats.</p>

      <p>This is work in progress, and there are several open issues still to be
      worked out. Although the available spellers and oxt's should work fine for
      the specified LibreOffice versions, please bear with us and report any
      issues you find to
      <a href="mailto:feedback@divvun.no">feedback@divvun.no</a></p>

      <note>In honour of the contributions by Tommi Pirinen to make these
      LibreOffice spell checkers come through, this download page is made
      public on the day of Tommi's public defense for his <a
      href="https://helda.helsinki.fi/handle/10138/42526">PhD on using
      Weighted Finite State technologies in spell checkers</a>.</note>

